<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>All Watches</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/collectionWatches.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/nav.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/footer.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/remixicon/4.6.0/remixicon.css" />
</head>

<body>


    <%- include('partials/header') %>
        <div id="collectionWatchesBanner" class="MECHAQUARTZ-banner">
            <div class="collectionWatchesContnet">
                <span>COLLECTION</span>
                <p>MECHAQUARTZ</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="collectionWatches">
            <p class="collectionWatches-title">MECHAQUARTZ</p>
            <div class="collectionWatcheswrapper">
                <% onlyMechaquartz.forEach(function(Mechaquartz){ %>
                    <div class="item">
                        <a href="/products/productDetail/<%= Mechaquartz._id %>">
                            <div class="image">
                                <img src="/uploads/<%= Mechaquartz.mainImage %>" alt="" class="main-item-image">
                                <img src="/uploads/<%= Mechaquartz.zoomImage %>" alt="" class="zoom-item-image">
                            </div>
                        </a>
                        <div class="itme-con">
                            <span class="item-name">
                                <%= Mechaquartz.name %>
                            </span>
                            <span class="item-price">USD <%= Mechaquartz.price %></span>
                            <a href="/products/productDetail/<%= Mechaquartz._id %>">
                                DISCOVER <i class="ri-arrow-right-s-fill"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <% }) %>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div id="MOVEMENT">
            <div class="MOVEMENT-section">
                <div class="MOVEMENT-image">
                    <img src="/assests/MECHAQUARTZ-img-2.jfif" alt="MOVEMENT">
                </div>
                <div class="MOVEMENT-text">
                    <span class="head-1">MOVEMENT</span>
                    <span class="head-2">MECHAQUARTZ, AN INTERESTING STORY TO TELL</span>
                    <div class="MOVEMENT-p-wrapper">
                        <p>
                            Also known as a hybrid movement, the so-called "Mecha-Quartz" offers the best of both worlds
                            â€” pairing the accuracy and reliability of Japanese quartz with a mechanical module that
                            delivers a sweeping seconds hand and an instant-reset chronograph. Originally developed
                            during the late 1980s in both Switzerland and Japan, this type of movement was pioneered by
                            Swiss companies like Piguet and LeCoultre to bring back the tactile feel of mechanical
                            chronographs in response to the quartz crisis. At Furlan Marri, we aim to revive this
                            innovative chapter in watchmaking history. One that belongs as much to Switzerland as it
                            does to Japan.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>

            <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/gsap.min.js"></script>
            <script src="/javascripts/nav.js"></script>
</body>

</html>